														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1650902">
									

<p>Wow, I love this tale!</p>
<p>The thing that really helps it is the earnest way the parents act. It's one thing to have crazy, brainwashed people act stereotypically; it's another to have them act with their normal personalities geared towards something vile, and it's great to read.</p>
<p>I did think Gunnar's scene was a bit of a weird transition with the parenthesis and general silliness.</p>
<p><a href="/scp-953">ALSO OH SHIT OH SHIT OH SHIT</a></p>

