														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1650908">
									

<p>I don't know if you've read the rest of Game Day, but the organization that Gunnar et al are a part of are basically incredibly enthusiastic poseurs. The ones who weren't good enough to get into one of the big GOIs, if they even know about any aside from the Foundation. And Gunnar is definitely a deliberate stereotype of a fratboy-ish metalhead kinda dumb teenager, with attendant fantasies. Because if one of them found out that magic and myths were real, but didn't have a very good grasp on anything but the &quot;sexy&quot; parts, he would jump all over the chance to live out his fantasies.</p>

							</div>

