<p>I saw this line. Stopped and thought to myself for a moment. Then just smiled because I knew exactly who that was and I am a big fan of that one and whatever tales they are in.</p>
<p>Anyway other than that I think personally that this is written very well! Though I'll mildly agree with Boulder above in that the Gunnar character is a little&#8230; Strange and personally seems a little bit out of place almost. Unless that's what you're going for here.</p>
<p><span style="font-size:xx-small;">Also when's the next/final part coming along?</span></p>

